":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/458322564","type":"question","created":1620440393,"answer_count":531,"follower_count":6243,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1576,5167,16866,19627,68732],"comment_count":47,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"也许很多人都听说过“中华八大原谅”，一个既接地气，又饱含新古典主义味道的概念。包括八个杀伤力巨大的传统词汇——不论遇到什么麻烦，人们甩出其中一个词汇，总能更容易得到原谅。 这八大原谅分别是：来都来了、给个面子、还是孩子、为了你好、习惯就好、大过节的、岁数大了、都不容易。 你人生中一定已经听过这些词不知多少次： “这景点人真多啊——哎，可是来都来了。” “他怎么打人啊——跟他计较啥呀，还是个孩子。” “外卖超时半小时都没送到——算了，都不容易。” 原谅他人之后，我们又会懊悔：凭什么原谅Ta？咋又是我吃了哑巴亏？ 不怪我方不争气，只怪敌方太狡猾。“八大原谅”之所以总能生效，其实是因为它们全部精准刺中了我们心理最软弱的一些弱点。 作者：简单心理 简单心理：用心理学解析“中华八大原谅”洗脑原理"},"attached_info":"Cj8IvIz+pJKRwec+EAMaCDY0MTI5Nzc4IMnq14QGMC844zBALHIJNDU4MzIyNTY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-46dcc128d48b04a08fb889bfe675271d_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1620529899.604868","card_id":"Q_457722320","target":{"id":457722320,"title":"《英雄联盟》里，你觉得什么话是对 AD 最大的侮辱？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457722320","type":"question","created":1620058803,"answer_count":180,"follower_count":242,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,1522,1538,4392,18427],"comment_count":6,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvIz+pJKRwec+EAMaCDYzOTk2MDU0ILPFwIQGMAY48gFALXIJNDU3NzIyMzIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5fbd5c3b7b8cd70f869cd11b49907020_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1620529899.6055446","card_id":"Q_458309120","target":{"id":458309120,"title":"参加今年（2021）的丘成桐大学生数学竞赛是怎样一种体验？","url